data.description: This 3 bedroom home has a fresh update including a new roof, new furnace, new flooring, fresh paint, new sidewalk, new crawlspace access, repairs to plumbing, new lighting and so much more. This home has a long Asphalt drive along the south side of the home that leads to a large 24' X 32' garage. Now, this home is looking for a NEW owner. This home is in move-in condition. Celebrate Christmas with the family in your new home.
